### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_token_aqui>
@deliveryId = <pega_el_id_del_delivery>

### ─────────────────────────────
### DELIVERIES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear delivery (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Juan",
  "phone": "2804207744"
}

###

### Crear otro delivery (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Pedro"
}

###

### Listar todos los deliveries
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener delivery por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/one?deliveryId={{deliveryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar delivery (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Juan P.",
  "phone": "2804207744",
  "active": true
}

###

### Desactivar delivery (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Juan P.",
  "phone": "2804207744",
  "active": false
}

###

### Eliminar delivery (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/{{deliveryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
